{"tid":869703,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會去烏克蘭玩?","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T14:30:26.000Z","uid":62252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f02b545ee953bcf0fdafa963caaa6dc7b6f0f84","tid":869703,"uid":62252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人會想去烏克蘭玩會需要烏克蘭幣?<br />\n<br />\n早排去烏克蘭玩完嚟<br />\n翻嚟個陣淨咗around 3~4000UAH (近成千蚊港紙)<br />\n唔記得喺機場換翻港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n翻到嚟先知原來呢個世界上除咗烏克蘭<br />\n係冇其他地方可以用到/換到做其他貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想搵到人同我唱翻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n呢啲國家唔似日本台灣<br />\n雖然真係好靚好玩又好平<br />\n(仲好多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )<br />\n我短期內(甚至呢世人)應該都唔會再去<br />\n<br />\n所以結論係<br />\n我真係好想搵到人同我唱翻啲錢做港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有意留個言好冇"},{"pid":"175f08fbe58dd0128a4710337d1de6f417d27573","tid":869703,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f02b545ee953bcf0fdafa963caaa6dc7b6f0f84","tid":869703,"uid":62252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人會想去烏克蘭玩會需要烏克蘭幣?<br />\n<br />\n早排去烏克蘭玩完嚟<br />\n翻嚟個陣淨咗around 3~4000UAH (近成千蚊港紙)<br />\n唔記得喺機場換翻港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n翻到嚟先知原來呢個世界上除咗烏克蘭<br />\n係冇其他地方可以用到/換到做其他貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想搵到人同我唱翻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no